      "updated": 1773766283225,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The single most important meta-skill: keep talking. Silence feels like uncertainty.\nNarrate your thinking even when you're unsure — \"I'm considering X because of Y, but\nthe downside is Z...\" is exactly what interviewers want to hear.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The single most important meta-skill: keep talking. Silence feels like uncertainty. Narrate your thinking even when you're unsure — \"I'm considering X because of Y, but the downside is Z...\" is exactly what interviewers want to hear.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
