      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Read \n- look up code in DB \n- return the short code if the the short code hasn't expired\n- and return with status code (302)\n\nWHY 302 and redirect?\n\n- 302 ( temporary redirect) - always ensures it goes through the DB \n- 301 (Permanent redirect) - browser caches response for the first time and later redirect on basis of the cached value ",
      "fontSize": 23.125434257988797,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Read \n- look up code in DB \n- return the short code if the the short code hasn't expired\n- and return with status code (302)\n\nWHY 302 and redirect?\n\n- 302 ( temporary redirect) - always ensures it goes through the DB \n- 301 (Permanent redirect) - browser caches response for the first time and later redirect on basis of the cached value ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
